        "content": "## Generate and store the MP3\nGenerate Sound Effect uses a Header Auth credential named ElevenLabs (header xi-api-key). The returned MP3 is uploaded to your Drive folder.",
        "color": 7,
        "width": 460,
        "height": 504
      }
    },
